---
interface Props {
}

const {} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
            <span class="bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full">Hızlı Erişim</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-roboto tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Köyümüz Hakkında
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 font-nunito text-gray-600">
            Aksu köyümüzün tarihi, doğal güzellikleri ve güncel gelişmeleri hakkında bilgi alabilirsiniz.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-y-16">
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-600">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                             stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                  d="M12 6.042A8.969 8.969 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/tarihce" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                        Köyümüzün Tarihçesi
                    </a>
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    1800'lü yıllara dayanan köklü geçmişimizi ve köyümüzün kuruluş hikayesini keşfedin.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-600">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                             stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                  d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/doga" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                        Doğal Güzellikler
                    </a>
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    Yemyeşil ormanları, serin suları ve eşsiz manzaralarıyla köyümüzün doğal zenginliklerini görün.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-600">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                             stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                  d="M12 7.5v9m7.5-1.5a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zM10.5 7.5a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zM10.5 12.75a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/haberler" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                        Güncel Haberler
                    </a>
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    Köyümüzdeki son gelişmelerden, etkinliklerden ve duyurulardan haberdar olun.
                </dd>
            </div>
        </dl>
    </div>
</div>